= SDL_GetWindowBrightness =
Use this function to get the brightness (gamma correction) for a window.


== Syntax ==
```c++
float SDL_GetWindowBrightness(SDL_Window* window)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the window to query
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns the last brightness value passed to [[SDL_SetWindowBrightness]]() on success, or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

